		<Relevance><![CDATA[(exists file "mswebdvd.dll" whose (version of it < "6.5.3790.4565") of it) of ( system wow64 folder)]]></Relevance>
		<Relevance>(not exists key "hklm\software\microsoft\updates\windows server 2003\sp3\kb973815" of x64 registry)</Relevance>
